app_description: Translator Go is very useful during work business trip and travel. It supports as many as 100 global languages such as English Japanese Chinese French Korean Spanish.... Using Translator Go you can easily scan translate: Official Paper Documents User Manuals Articles from Books Magazines Menus in Restaurants Instructions Texts on Product Labels Road Signs and more... Main Features of Translator Foto: 1 Support 100 languages 2 Voice Translation Take photos or import images from camera roll Choose adjust and crop texts from photos or images Convert image format into text format Translate text instantly 3 Text Translation: copy text or input manually 4 Photo Translation 5 Edit copy share text or translation 6 Check history favorite Paid packages and prices Subscription information. 1. Monthly subscription instructions: Subscription period: 1 month subscription price: 4.99 month automatically renewed. 2. Quarterly subscription instructions: Subscription period: 3 months subscription price: 9.99 3 months automatically renewed. 3. Annual subscription instructions: Subscription period: 1 year. Subscription price: 19.99 year automatically renewed. If you don t want to subscribe you can unsubscribe at any time. Payment will be charged to your iTunes account at confirmation of purchase. Subscription automatically renews unless you cancel at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period. After purchasing a subscription you can manage and cancel the subscription in the account settings of the App Store. If a free trial is offered any unused portion will be forfeited when you purchase a subscription to that publication.
